snippet.title: Free maze game cellbreach v1.1 a new 2d java game update
snippet.description:
Free maze game cellbreach v1.1 a new 2d java game update
development: http://www.cellbreach.com

Current video is an update to cellbreach v1.1
A cube maze game with death in all corners.
This is a multiplayer java game for windows or mac.
Do you like puzzles and mazes ? well this is the game for you!

The game is in development, but all is welcome to check it out if you wish.

Visit www.cellbreach.com to play for free :D
